    <bodyTop>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>This guide gives you advice on dealing with both crises and more everyday situations. It has been produced to:</p>
<ol>
<li>Help you to recognise when a student may be in difficulty.</li>
<li>Provide advice to help you respond/refer appropriately and effectively.</li>
<li>Remind you of the sources of support within the University and in the Community.</li>
<li>Raise awareness of issues relating to student mental health.</li>
</ol>]]></Value>
    </bodyTop>
